{"tid":258333,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人做緊傳媒行業?","createTime":"2017-05-26T04:32:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-26T18:38:10.000Z","uid":47584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9251792d3e42b633e7cc6356860382307416c120","tid":258333,"uid":47584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T04:32:36.000Z","msg":"呢行係咪倒退/停滯得好勁?<br />\n<br />\n紙媒受網媒挑戰<br />\n網媒又因為結構鬆散而非常唔穩定<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另外<br />\n傳媒行業既人工真係同世界脫節咁<br />\nStarting同其他行業差唔多<br />\n但係其他行業起碼都有條career path<br />\n傳媒真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有無行內人過嚟講下真實情況?<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 利申:八大普通文科fg,想入傳媒<br />\n但係睇到個人工+前景真係有啲縮沙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"978f63afe6bf553096bb781858e4b95e5e9cb45d","tid":258333,"uid":55296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T05:42:48.000Z","msg":"你想入media 嘅乜嘢？"},{"pid":"37786a28b7dc8c4a8dc25aa895368c88efeddd1a","tid":258333,"uid":42007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T05:54:05.000Z","msg":"隔離有個記者post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"710aa2c5a99d222c22873c515134f57865037a1b","tid":258333,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T05:57:10.000Z","msg":"傳統媒體學生（演藝 傳理）<br />\n細個只系 揀 TVB一個台梨睇<br />\n大個只系得TVB一個台可以 揀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n創意媒體<br />\n當市場充斥 content farm, YouTuber, Facebook pages<br />\n大公司再唔需要一team人做digital marketing<br />\n而系外判畀製作公司（Umovie, 毛記電視）<br />\n甚到搵YouTuber做代言人(KOL)已經可以搞到好有noise"},{"pid":"376bb287556a9346a629b796e4639b3f2c30fce5","tid":258333,"uid":81906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T08:04:31.000Z","msg":"不